WEBVTT

00:04.212 --> 00:07.545
HOW DO I LOVE THEE,
LET ME CALL YOU BACK

00:07.712 --> 00:09.755
A gift.

00:10.421 --> 00:13.547
- Who's it for?
- It's for Harry.

00:13.714 --> 00:16.966
Why are you giving a gift
to that conman?

00:17.132 --> 00:22.760
To pay him back for conning us. Coach
found a trick wallet in a novelty shop.

00:22.927 --> 00:28.720
What you do is you open it up
and flames come right up to your face.

00:28.887 --> 00:33.514
- Isn't this a little crueI?
- It's harmless, really.

00:33.681 --> 00:36.556
That's why we didn't give it to you.

00:36.723 --> 00:39.349
He's coming. Here he comes.

00:43.267 --> 00:46.519
- Am I glad to see you, Harry.
- You are?

00:46.686 --> 00:51.145
Are you kidding me?
You are a valued customer and a friend.

00:51.312 --> 00:56.315
I was feeling bad about all the times
I kicked you out of here.

00:56.482 --> 00:59.400
- It's from all of us.
- For me?

00:59.565 --> 01:02.817
Gosh,
I never expected anything like this.

01:02.983 --> 01:08.653
No one's ever given me anything
voluntarily. Shall I save it for Christmas?

01:08.819 --> 01:12.529
No. Please, Harry. Open it now.
It's a hot one.

01:17.280 --> 01:20.365
- A wallet!
- It's just a little gesture.

01:20.532 --> 01:23.950
- It's beautifuI.
- I can't wait.

01:24.117 --> 01:27.368
I'm so touched.

01:27.535 --> 01:29.577
Don't mention it.

01:29.744 --> 01:33.079
- Aren't you going to open it?
- Sure.

01:33.246 --> 01:36.956
Back from your face a little,
so we can all see.

01:42.165 --> 01:46.792
- It was funnier in the store.
- There must be 60 bucks here.

01:46.959 --> 01:51.670
You guys are too much.
I'll never forget this. Thanks a lot.

01:54.920 --> 01:59.005
