We can scout the tickets at the arena.

03:27.290 --> 03:30.790
OK. I'll pay. I'll pay the $200.

03:30.957 --> 03:35.585
Give me my purse.
It's still exorbitant for a prizefight.

03:35.751 --> 03:40.003
It's Marvin Hagler.
It's the prizefight of the year.

03:40.920 --> 03:43.337
I assume that a cheque will do.

03:44.213 --> 03:49.214
Anything. Make it out to PhiI Keppler,
MedicaI Corporation.

03:51.716 --> 03:56.134
I thought I recognised
that naturaI compassion, Doctor.

