20:43.421 --> 20:45.881
Ditto?

20:46.048 --> 20:49.965
You're telling me
I waited a week for "ditto"?

20:50.131 --> 20:52.467
You took my answer.

20:54.759 --> 20:56.927
All right, I'm sorry.

20:57.927 --> 21:01.928
No more stalling.
I'll just tell you right here.

21:06.681 --> 21:12.975
I couldn't come up with anything.
I'm sorry. I really wanted to do this.

21:13.140 --> 21:19.561
I don't understand. I'm usually so good
under pressure, but I just drew a blank.

21:21.811 --> 21:27.064
Honey,
I have no idea why we're together.

21:32.899 --> 21:35.316
Neither do I.

21:37.317 --> 21:40.193
- You don't?
- I don't have a clue.

21:40.360 --> 21:44.612
- What about what you just said?
- I read it in a book.

21:45.987 --> 21:49.239
It sounded nice, but it's not us.

21:50.322 --> 21:54.031
- Is it?
- I don't know. I wasn't listening.

21:56.450 --> 22:01.451
Please, whatever we do right now,
don't say, "What are we doing?"

22:01.618 --> 22:05.411
What are we doing
that I can't say what are we doing?

22:05.577 --> 22:09.037
