reason I'm with you is because I lo...

22:24.335 --> 22:27.128
What, Sam?

22:27.294 --> 22:31.005
I said the reason
why I'm with you is cos I lo...

22:32.171 --> 22:36.882
- You lo...?
- You know what I mean.

22:37.049 --> 22:41.550
- What's the matter? Can't you say it?
- Of course. I lo...

22:44.552 --> 22:50.095
Don't you see? That phrase
that you throw around so casually

22:50.262 --> 22:52.971
is now impossible for you to say.

22:53.138 --> 22:57.848
Why can't you say it?
Because with me, it's no longer casuaI.

22:58.932 --> 23:02.642
I'm important to you. I matter.

